{
  "chapter": 36,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十六回「人中之龙」。七大门派掌门人连袂现身泰山大会，铁髯道长、无相大师等当众审问石不为。公孙不智以诈死之计揭露石不为之罪行——石不为暗中主谋杀兄灭口，妄图夺取武林权柄。石不为被逼认罪后拒透露幕后大哥大姐的身份，以恶毒诅咒恐吓群豪后服毒自尽。铁神龙悲愤欲以死谢罪，被无相大师制止。麻衣老人暗中毁去火药引线消除隐患，无相大师以慈悲为怀释放火魔神。方宝玉获群豪拥戴，七派掌门齐声赞誉，称之为人中之龙。铁娃兴奋异常，群豪纷纷请方宝玉展示武艺。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_qun_hao",
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "text": "铁髯道长……原来是铁髯道长。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_dang_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "武当弟子",
      "listener": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "text": "弟子参见掌门祖师。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "text": "你……是你老人家……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你老人家莫非是……是……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "无相",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老僧正是无相。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qun_hao",
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "少林掌门人也来了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "text": "弟子参见掌门大师。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "第三人",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "孽障，还认得我么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_tie_shen_long",
      "text": "弟子不知恩师你老人家也来了，弟子……弟子……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "铁髯道长",
      "listener": "char_wu_dang_di_zi",
      "text": "本门弟子，毋庸多礼……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "铁髯道长",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "少林、峨嵋、昆仑、点苍、崆峒、淮阳门下弟子，也站起来吧，难道你们要在地上跪一辈子么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "铁髯道长",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "石不为，谁叫你站起来的？你还是跪下。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "无相大师",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "铁髯道兄令别人全都勿需多礼，却偏偏令你一人跪着，你心中可是有些不服之意么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "text": "弟子不敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "无相大师",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "你可知道这是为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "text": "弟子不知。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "铁髯道长",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "你还不知？在无相大师面前，你也敢说假话？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弟子真的不知……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "铁髯道长",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "你师父费了七年心血，总算将你调教成一条能在江湖间站得起来的汉子，你怎可做出此等恶毒之事，你对得起人么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弟子做了何事？……弟子犯了何罪？弟子实在不知，但望……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "铁髯道长",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "住口！你既已犯下滔天大罪，此刻便该痛心疾首，自责自悔，不想你竟然还敢妄图狡赖！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非你老人家也相信了别人对弟子的诬蔑之词，难道……难道各位师伯师叔都不相信弟子，反而相信别人？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_mei_ao_tian",
      "text": "梅师伯……王师叔……你们两位一向对弟子最为爱护，如今难道眼见弟子含冤难伸，也不为弟子洗刷？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "无相大师",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "不错，此事死无对证，全无凭据，你不肯承认，谁也无法判你之罪。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这本是他们血口喷人，虚空捏造，自然绝无证据。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "铁髯道长",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "畜牲，你只当你这事真的做得天衣无缝，全无破绽么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弟子根本……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "铁髯道长",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "我若不叫你死心，你也不肯服罪。好！你且瞧瞧……",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "铁髯道长",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你且瞧瞧他是谁？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "text": "你……你还未死？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "不错，我还未死，老五那一掌之力，又怎能致我于死？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "text": "但他却非以掌力伤你，而是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "不错，老五并非以掌力伤我，而是用的见血封喉之绝毒暗器。但此事你又怎会知道的？莫非你在旁边瞧见了么？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我只是猜……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "事已至此，你还不说实话？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "text": "你故意陷人人罪，我无话可说。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "好，我不妨再告诉你，自从老七、老二、老六相继遇害之后，我便已将本门护身金丝马甲穿在身上，老五发出的那些暗器虽然狠毒，但只能击穿我外面的衣衫，却丝毫未曾伤及我的皮肉。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我也……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "老四，不想你又说漏嘴了。我自窗内飞出时，你藏身窗下，又曾补了我一掌，但我那时既然未中暗器，你那一掌，只不过仅使我略受伤损而已，若想致我于死，还差得远哩！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "text": "但你……你又为何……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "你深知老五性情，贪黠有余，气魄却不足，要想做出这样的恶事，他还没有这么大的胆子。暗中主谋的，必定另有其人。我为了要探查出这人是谁，是以虽然未中暗器，却作出重伤之态。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "但我却当真未曾想到，伏身窗下的竟然是你。我早就说过，我兄弟七人之中，你的城府最深，也最难对付……若是换了别人，我那时便要揭破你们的奸谋，但既然是你，我就不敢轻举妄动了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "只因我深知那时我若有所动作，只有招来你的毒手，那时我与大哥实是人单势孤，你暗中却不知有多少帮手，我纵能约得一些武林同道，也未见是你之敌，何况，那时根本就未必会有人相助于我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "更何况，我早已算准了你必定会将老五杀之灭口，于是你自然便不得不留下大哥的活命，以免别人怀疑于你。大哥的安危既无危险，我便索性将计就计，装着伤重不支，落荒而逃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "text": "莫非那……那具尸身也是你的……你的……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "不错，那具尸身也是我的疑兵之计。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "text": "尸身？……什么尸身？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "我逃走之后，算定我的惊呼必已惊动大哥，石不为便肯定不致立时追来。那时万竹山庄中正是群豪毕集，有贤也有不肖，我便寻了个平日声名最最狼藉之徒，将他诱出，点了他穴道，将我穿的衣服换在他身上，又将那些毒药暗器射在他背后……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "text": "但他的面目终是与你不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "我本待在他面上划些伤痕，涂些污泥，哪知那些暗器委实太过霸道，那人中了暗器之后，手足四肢，面目五官，竟俱都立刻肿了起来，肤色也变为黑紫，七窍俱都破裂，流得满面是血，根本不需我再做手脚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "好厉害……好狠毒！石不为呀石不为，你又怎忍心下得了如此毒手。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我方自安排妥当，便听得有脚步之声过来。我走也来不及了，便伏身躲在暗中，只见来的便是石不为。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那时我犹自不能完全断定他便是主恶之凶，是以便索性屏息静气，瞧个究竟。但他……他见到那具尸身之后，面上果然露出狂喜之色，竟……竟在我那具尸身上又狠狠刺了两剑。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "公孙不智",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到那时我心中才断定无疑，但仍猜不出他为何对我那般怀恨。只见他一剑刺下，连剑身都变为乌黑颜色。那时四下无人，他便将那尸身与长剑俱都以衣衫包起，悄悄抬走，也不知是被他抛人河沟中还是被他掩埋，而我……唉！我便连夜赶回武当，却不想各位师伯师叔也都在那里。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "无相大师",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_bu_zhi",
      "text": "好了，下面的话，你已不必再说。这孽障想必总是已将恶贯满盈，是以苍天才令我们这些已有多年未曾出山的老头子一齐聚在武当。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "铁神龙",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "孽障，你还有何话说？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，好，昔日白三空常说咱们这些人里，若论智计，谁也比不上公孙不智，那时我暗中还不服，直到如今我才服了，服了。我石不为自问行事周密，哪知却还是栽在你这小狐狸手里。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "铁神龙",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "畜牲，事已至此，你还不痛悔求饶？你还敢如此无礼？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事已至此，我痛悔求饶又有何用？莫非你们还饶得了我？不错，那些人是我宰了的，你们要怎样，只管来吧！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "如意老人",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "此时此刻，反正再也不怕他能逃上天去，你我不如将此事完全问个清楚，再出手也还不迟。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_mei_ao_tian",
      "text": "什么事石某都已承当，你还有什么好问的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "如意老人",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "我深知你的为人，一些金银财帛决不能打动于你，你究竟是为了什么才做出这样的事来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_mei_ao_tian",
      "text": "问得好……问得好，世上总算已有一人相信，我石不为不是任何人的威胁利诱所能打得动的。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "铁神龙",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "那你是为了什么……说！快说呀！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥、大姐，你们要我做的事，我都已做了，只恨未能做好而已……还没有做好的事，还没杀的仇人，只有等你们去杀了，小弟在九泉之下，必定化为厉鬼，在暗中相助于你们。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "铁神龙",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "谁是你的大哥、大姐？谁是你的仇人？你本是孤儿，又有什么血海深仇？你……你……你究竟是为了什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪些是我的仇人？我究竟是为了什么？这些事我死也不会说的……我要叫你们糊里糊涂，暗中猜疑，直到我大哥大姐的复仇之剑刺人你们身上时你们才会明白，但那时……哈哈！那时已太迟了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁是我大哥么？……可能是你，也可能是他，这擂台之上，人人都有可能，你们猜去吧！你们越是互相猜疑，我大哥便是方便，但你们能忍得住不去猜疑么？……哈哈……哈哈……哈哈……",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "铁神龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "第七代掌门弟子铁神龙，禀告在天各位祖师之灵，弟子不肖，教诲无方，以致第八代弟子石不为竟背叛门规，作恶江湖，不幸此不肖恶徒死时仍为本门弟子，竟未及将之逐出门墙……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "铁神龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弟子恨不能在其生前时将之正以门规，只有等他死后戮尸，以正门规。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "铁神龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本门门户不幸，出此叛徒，弟子实已难逃其责，弟子……",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "铁髯道长",
      "listener": "char_tie_shen_long",
      "text": "你……你这是何苦？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 391,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "铁神龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我教徒无方，非但对不起本门师长，也对不起各位，我若不死，我……我怎能心安，怎能谢罪？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "铁髯道长",
      "listener": "char_tie_shen_long",
      "text": "胡说，此事谁能怪你？普天之下，又有谁会怪你？武林风云激荡，正值需人之际，你……你怎能轻言一死？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 399,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_shen_long",
      "speaker_name": "铁神龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我……两位放了我吧！我……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "无相大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此刻他心情太过激动，还是让他安睡片刻的好……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 409,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们此刻想必已知道，金不畏等人并非由某家主谋所害的了，为何还如此眼睁睁地看某家？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 421,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "铁髯道长",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "既非你主谋，你方才为何要承认？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "某家方才若不承认，岂不是要害死方宝玉？事急从权，古有明训，这……各位莫非还不知道么？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 427,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "某家言已尽此，你等要将某家怎样，只管说出便是。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 435
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "无相大师",
      "listener": "char_ding_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "老夫人有何高见？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 441,
      "line_end": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "丁老夫人",
      "listener": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "text": "但凭大师定夺。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 443,
      "line_end": 443
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "无相大师",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "方少侠意下如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 445,
      "line_end": 445
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "text": "大师慈悲，弟子怎敢妄言。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 449,
      "line_end": 451
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "无相大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，侠义之心，慈悲为主。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 453,
      "line_end": 453
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "无相大师",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "去吧，快快去吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 455,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "即是如此，某家告辞了。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 465,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "铁髯道长",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 467,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "text": "怎样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 469,
      "line_end": 469
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "铁髯道长",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "无相大师本我佛心肠，今日饶过了你，你非但毫无感激之意，竟还敢作出如此猖狂之态？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 471,
      "line_end": 473
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "text": "某家为何要有感激之意？你等不敢拦阻于我，只不过是畏惧某家那足可令人粉身碎骨的火药而已，你等若敢对某家……",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 475,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "火药俱是藏在山林隐处的棺木之中，此刻引线已被老夫毁去，魔宫弟子也被老夫制住，隐患已除，各位只管放心吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 479,
      "line_end": 481
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "铁髯道长",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "此番又怎样？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 491,
      "line_end": 491
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "text": "你要怎样？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 493,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "无相大师",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "火施主，你只当老僧方才放你是为了有所畏惧于你么？你错了……错了，此时此刻，我等如要取你性命，实如足踏蝼蚁一般，纵然火药还在，你也绝无可能发出号令，此点你莫非还不相信？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 499,
      "line_end": 503
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "无相大师",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "去吧！你还是去吧！老僧但望你以此余生做些有益人群之事，至于听与不听，却全都在你了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 507,
      "line_end": 509
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "一言之诺，万金不易，你放心吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 515,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "好，三日之后，自来相见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 517,
      "line_end": 519
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "铁髯道长",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "纵虎归山，必有后患。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 523,
      "line_end": 523
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "无相大师",
      "listener": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "text": "杀之失仁，放之取义。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 525,
      "line_end": 525
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "铁髯道长",
      "listener": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "text": "大师说的是，铁髯错了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 527,
      "line_end": 527
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "text": "多谢前辈此番……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_xiang_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "无相大师",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "老僧今日得见人中之龙，实觉当为江湖庆幸……阿弥陀佛，我佛慈悲，如今泥污已洗，宝珠当可大放光明。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 535,
      "line_end": 537
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ran_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "铁髯道长",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "大师说的是……方宝玉，你切莫忘了大师教诲，好自为之，今日之江湖，已是你纵马逐鹿的时候了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 539,
      "line_end": 541
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多谢教诲。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 543,
      "line_end": 543
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_tie_wa",
      "speaker_name": "铁娃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥好，有这样的大哥真好。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 561,
      "line_end": 563
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qun_hao",
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "请方少侠露手功夫让咱们开开眼界。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 565,
      "line_end": 567
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qun_hao",
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "请方少侠露手功夫让咱们瞧瞧，请方少侠……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 569,
      "line_end": 569
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位……各位……在下……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 571,
      "line_end": 571
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "如意老人",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
